Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill records the physical function capability of a person by administering a PROMIS Physical Function test called short form 4a. The participant is asked 4 questions one at a time. For each question, the participant has 5 specific phrase choices. We are developing the skills for Pharmaceutical and Biotech companies and this is one illustration of a public skill. This skill is not affiliated with live clinical trials.
